➜【星连文学社】宽哥：《鹧鸪天.庆八一》
http://www.sohu.com/a/410951200_100115135	35983
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200801/05cecbd5d4664c89b281868c8cc67a9c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《鹧鸪天.庆八一》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong> 文/宽哥</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>庆祝中国人民解放军建军93周年！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鲜艳军旗血染红，南昌起义炮声隆。灭豺驱虎逐倭寇，一唱东方天下雄。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">听党令，祷精忠。历兵沙场奋争锋。担当使命心牢记，待旦枕戈建懋功。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200801/289597f57c434aac997f97cf721e0d82.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200801/47db92d0bb404afb84997ef69cac167d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
